  "professional_suggestions": [
    "Condense the Core Competencies and Technical Skills sections to focus on the most relevant tools for the target role, removing redundant or peripheral items.",
    "Add a brief ‘Key Achievements’ bullet under each role that highlights a specific challenge, the action you took, and the measurable result to give context to the impressive metrics.",
    "Include a concise soft‑skills paragraph or examples (e.g., stakeholder management, cross‑functional collaboration) to balance the heavy emphasis on hard metrics and show leadership depth."
